comments: I did not notice anything different, I first memorised the last letter of the alien alphabet and associated with the images, then I associated the middle letter with the shape of the object. I do not know if that is what you are looking for in my answers. I found it really hard to see the words in such little time, I would always look for the ending of the word, if it ended with an inverted triangle, something close to tb and a stick with 2 hanging from the right side.
